From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Wed, 4 Mar 2026 07:08:41 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 57/66] Add Plusium C++ browser binary
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Four hundred lines of C++ code,
Linking libtermsurf_content's load.
No profile server in sight—
Just sockets, protobuf, done right.
The old guard's crumbling abode.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
